headline: Texas Instruments board declares second quarter 2025 quarterly dividend
summary: The board of directors of Texas Instruments Incorporated (Nasdaq: TXN) today declared a quarterly cash dividend of $1.36 per share of common stock, payable May 13, 2025, to stockholders of record on April 30, 2025.

headline: This chip stock ’is clearly the most popular long’, Citi says (not Nvidia)
